title: Garrys.Mod.Server.v14.07.08
description:
This is a complete server package, just download and start it.
It contains the following:

* GMOD Server v14.07.08 (cracked)
* Scripts for updating and cracking
* Instructions for how to add addons and game content
* GWTool v0.3

More information on how to customize it can be found on the Internet.

If you get an error about a missing DLL file, install this (choose x86): <a href="
http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=30679" rel="nofollow" target="_NEW">
http://www.microsoft.com/en-us/download/details.aspx?id=30679</a>

These files are provided AS-IS and I won't provide any more support for them. If you can't get it to work you probably don't have sufficient knowledge to run a server either.
